= Example node.json = 
* Cloud controller

<pre>
{ "run_list": [
  "recipe[cloud-common]",
  "recipe[cloud-controller]"
  ] 
}
</pre>

* Compute node
<pre>
{ "run_list": [
  "recipe[cloud-common]",
  "recipe[compute-node]"
  ] 
}
</pre>

* Cloud controller is also compute node (all in one)
<pre>
{ "run_list": [
  "recipe[cloud-common]",
  "recipe[cloud-controller]",
  "recipe[compute-node]"
  ] 
}
</pre>



